ync\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-64674 size-medium\" style=\"margin-top: 55px;\" src=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/images\/the-automatic-millionaire-book-195x300.jpg\" alt=\"the automatic millionaire\" width=\"195\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/images\/the-automatic-millionaire-book-195x300.jpg 195w, https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/images\/the-automatic-millionaire-book-550x848.jpg 550w, https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/images\/the-automatic-millionaire-book-324x500.jpg 324w, https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/images\/the-automatic-millionaire-book.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 195px) 100vw, 195px\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<td valign=\"center\"><a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/3wUUFzx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>The Automatic Millionaire<\/strong><\/a> by <strong>David Bach<\/strong> &#8212; This is my 3rd favorite financial book, and one I refused to read for quite some time. Just seemed too fluffy and &#8220;look how easy it is to do!&#8221; type deal. But after being bored one day and sucking it up, I was VERY glad I did :) It&#8217;s kinda basic and on the lighter side, but if you&#8217;re one who needs someone to tell you exactly what to do in detail &#8211; and you&#8217;re going to listen! &#8211; you&#8217;d be on the fast track to wealth in no time. Perfect for a\u00a0 beginner.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\" width=\" 200\"><a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/3wX0w7o\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-64675 size-full\" style=\"margin-top: 65px;\" src=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/images\/the-richest-man-in-babylon.jpg\" alt=\"the richest man in babylon\" width=\"227\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/images\/the-richest-man-in-babylon.jpg 227w, https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/images\/the-richest-man-in-babylon-170x300.jpg 170w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 227px) 100vw, 227px\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<td style=\"padd