/mo)&#8211; Similar to Opportun, this app helps you automatically INVEST money vs savings by rounding up all your transactions to the nearest dollar and then dropping it right in for you &#8211; don&#8217;t even have to think about it! You sign up once, connect your accounts, and it takes it from there. It stashed $400 for me while trying it in only a short amount of time &#8211; works well. My full review of Acorns can be found <a href=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/2015\/03\/acorns-app-review\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here<\/a>.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"center\"><a href=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/go\/honey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-64826 size-full\" style=\"margin-top: 40px;\" src=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/images\/honey-icon.jpg\" alt=\"honey\" width=\"512\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/images\/honey-icon.jpg 512w, https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/images\/honey-icon-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/images\/honey-icon-125x125.jpg 125w, https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/images\/honey-icon-500x500.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<td valign=\"center\"><a href=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/go\/honey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Honey<\/strong><\/a> (FREE) &#8212; By far my favorite coupon service out there!! Any time I&#8217;m about to check out and buy something online, I click the Honey button in my browser and it automatically scours the &#8216;net for all coupons and applies the *best* one immediately to save me the most money. It literally takes seconds and I never have to Google for them anymore :) (Though it doesn&#8217;t always find any coupons). You can see my write up on them <a href=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/save-money-using-honey-browser-extension\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">h